  "detailed_description": "<strong>Hail to the King</strong> is a strategic single-player puzzle game. Move your pieces across a board of crumbling tiles.  Find the safest path and get your King to the other side.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/c53d0dc8d3e761e85ff2b8064266304f.poster.avif?t=1572667752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/c53d0dc8d3e761e85ff2b8064266304f.webm?t=1572667752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/c53d0dc8d3e761e85ff2b8064266304f.mp4?t=1572667752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 unique levels<br></li><li> Collect 3 stars per level for bonus points<br></li><li> Gems reveal adjacent trapped tiles<br></li><li> Avoid Hidden Traps<br></li><li> Knights, Bishops, Rooks and Queens can be sacrificed to crumble tiles in a familiar pattern.<br></li><li> Localization for 12 Languages<br></li><li> Sharpen your memory skills!<br></li><li> Protect the King!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/63c38574384b8f1d66e184547b2868dd.poster.avif?t=1572667752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/63c38574384b8f1d66e184547b2868dd.webm?t=1572667752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998730/extras/63c38574384b8f1d66e184547b2868dd.mp4?t=1572667752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
